			"sort":0,
			"flags":{},
			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<p><b>Standard Action</b></p><p><b>Close</b> burst 1</p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Target: </b> Each creature in burst</p><p class=\"power-basics\"><b>Attack: </b>+22 vs. Reflex; two attacks</p><p><b>Miss: </b> The target is flung 30 feet into the air, then falls back down. It takes 3d10 damage and falls prone in a random square within 3 squares of its starting position.</p><p><b>Miss: </b> The target slides to an unoccupied square adjacent to the burst. If no such square is available, the attack hits automatically.</p><p><b>Effect: </b> The burst creates an area of difficult terrain.</p>",
